In an ever changing world, I appreciate living on an island. The idea of getting up and enjoying what our island naturally offers get me through some days, from enjoying our beaches to capturing moments of families enjoying the beach. Sustaining our beaches for me is encouraging my clients to only take pictures instead of what they see in our sands and seas. Leaving nature in place  helps me to continue being a photographer.
